    • Constructor Detail

      • Tour

        public Tour(Chauffeur chauffeur,
            Bus bus,
            Schedule schedule,
            boolean food)
        Four-argument constructor. Initializes the seats array and constructs new Seat objects according to bus seat numbers. Reservations variable is initialized as an arraylist. The schedule for the tour is added to the bus' and chaffeur's schedules.
        Parameters:
        chauffeur - the chauffeur as a Chauffeur object
        bus - the bus as a Bus object
        schedule - the schedule as a Schedule object
        food - the food as a boolean
